{"tid":1431784,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警 昨日(7/8)記招 與 前一晚(6/8) 口供不同 !","createTime":"2019-08-08T05:28:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T06:31:25.000Z","uid":280464,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"80e25f9c31b30922441ff33d27cdfd3ada546fe8","tid":1431784,"uid":280464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:28:22.000Z","msg":"前一晚(6/8 11:00PM) 總督察周學賢 話果<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">5名探員係經過，見到一名男子啱啱離開排檔</span></span></strong>，覺得形跡可疑先截查被捕人。<br />\n<br />\n但昨日 (7/8 4:00PM) 記招 高級警司李貴華 休班同事<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">見到可疑男子同檔主誰詢緊一支好強力的雷射鎗，傾完仲試完仲見到購買完放落膠袋到</span></span></strong>，所以見到佢形跡可疑先截查被捕人&hellip;&hellip;&hellip; <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請問 : 警方是否作假口供 ? </span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"595b0e6e937ac92557fbcb895ada7603d7c6d488","tid":1431784,"uid":280464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:29:15.000Z","msg":"自堆"},{"pid":"c4c80c2148d8a865a54194eb55f921ae5cfdcc6a","tid":1431784,"uid":280464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:29:32.000Z","msg":"自堆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30696f42f249bd23a7fab77b07cbc4b8d3ffbf8f","tid":1431784,"uid":66221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:29:46.000Z","msg":"駛唔駛推到民間記招叫警犬1600覆機？"},{"pid":"84901a4d0b926e93a1a6d1670ae0aa2ff79a62d4","tid":1431784,"uid":280464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:29:59.000Z","msg":"自堆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/nor